Hail visitors, and well met!  I welcome you to my home.  Please, sit by the fire and warm yourself.  I'm well aware that those of you who are not of my race may be chilled by our colder climate.

Do make yourself at home, for there is much to see.  Take heed of the featured original art section of my home, for wonderful paintings by talented individuals can be found.  Perhaps you'd prefer to find information about members of your own race?   If so, I welcome you to visit my "Inhabitants of Norrath" archive.   For there you will find a list of visitors who have left their mark so others may seek them out.  Some have even left paintings or other artifacts which depict them in this or other realms.

I always welcome and appreciate your comments and suggestions.  For if I can make you more comfortable here, then I have been blessed by the gods which I serve.

Something New!

This may or may not be a first.  However, I've created a Microsoft Plus! theme based on our wonderful world of EverQuest.  You can download the theme here.  Any and all feedback is appreciated.  The size of this download is about 2.5MB.  And that's without a lot of sounds.  The actual music came from files found on EQVault in MP3 format (then decoded to WAV for the theme).  Some other sounds, like the bear growl, dog barking, snake rattle, and whip, came from various places across the net.  I've put in some good parts of the music for the start-up and shutdown sequences, and emptying of the recycle bin.  So, check it out and let me know what you think.
